nodes.text: Oteroa Zero-Twenty was the twentieth city produced by OteroaCorp to assist their orbiting refinery ship, The Oteroan Sky, from the ground. The city was located on Dathomir, and was also known to its residents as "Zero-Twenty" or "ZT." The city was located in the Dathomiri jungle near the Nardithi Cluster, and was heavily fortified. Oteroa Zero-Twenty was eventually destroyed when The Oteroan Sky crashed into it from orbit.
